Class DefaultSubject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.truth.Subject
      • com.google.common.truth.DefaultSubject
  • Deprecated. 
    Use plain Subject instead. At the moment, Subject has type parameters, so you may wish to use Subject<?, ?>. However, those type parameters will soon go away, so you may wish to start using raw Subject now to prepare.
